data.description: Victorian stunner in the heart of Mt. Washington! Steps away from local attractions, the overlook & incline on Grandview. So many possibilities with this property. Use it as a huge single family home with two kitchens 5 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms. Use it as a true duplex; unit 1 a 1br 1ba on the first floor and unit 2 a 4br 2ba on the 2nd and 3rd floors; live in one and rent out the other. Or use it as a short term furnished rental! This home boasts a large backyard to enjoy summer evenings by a fire pit, those famous Mt. Washington views of the city, beautiful hardwood floors, amazing original woodwork throughout, three levels of living space, a back deck to sip your morning coffee, 2nd floor laundry, and charm out the wazoo! Do not miss out on this rare opportunity!
